en_201213_0	The chief incumbent of Warakaapola Naa Sevena Sadaham Ashramaya, Suriyawewa Sumedha Thera says that there is no conspiracy to have see the assassination of the former president, Mahinda Rajapaksa or former defence secretary, Gotabhaya Rajapaksa.
en_201213_1	Media reports published in the last few weeks stating that Namal Kumara, who exposed the conspiracy, had set out to organize a ceremony under the patronage of former president Rajapaksa and former defence secretary Gotabhaya Rajapaksa.
en_201213_2	However, Suriyawewa Sumedha Thera believes that there was no such assassination conspiracy.
